       |  |                            Level 7 ($007c) $xxxxxx    |  |
       |  |                                                       |  |
       |  |  DRIVE STATUS: xxxxxx xxxx xxxxxxxx                   |  |
       |  |                                                       |  |
       |  |  System Time : xxxxxxx   Date: xxxxxxx                |  |
